				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p133293">Re: The NES vs. its contemporary competition</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=133293#p133293"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Aug 30, 2014 8:17 am&nbsp;</div></td>
